titles.title: A bill to revise the boundaries of certain John H. Chafee Coastal Barrier Resources System units in New Jersey.
A bill to revise the boundaries of certain John H. Chafee Coastal Barrier Resources System units in New Jersey.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Environment and Public Works.

bill.summary: This bill modifies certain boundaries of the John H. Chafee Coastal Barrier Resources System Units located in Middlesex and Monmouth Counties, New Jersey.
